    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "It’s a rather bad sleep with mosquitos and waking up to quite a lot of children noises. We take a very slow start - not in any rush to get to Dedza until the afternoon. We each breakfast on the bench in the sand and a couple terrifying spiders make their way onto our heads.",
            "link": null
          },
