    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "And as we leave Mufasa we stop. Jordan has suggested that I take a look at the small wooden tractors that they are selling on the side of the road. I stop for curtesy’s sake, but without much desire of buying anything… UNTIL I SEE THE TRACTOR. It’s a perfect scale replica of a frontend loader with ingenious functional hydraulic pistons made from wood. I must have this (I love tractors).",
            "link": null
          },
          "annotations": {
            "bold": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false,
            "code": false,
            "color": "default"
          },
          "plain_text": "And as we leave Mufasa we stop. Jordan has suggested that I take a look at the small wooden tractors that they are selling on the side of the road. I stop for curtesy’s sake, but without much desire of buying anything… UNTIL I SEE THE TRACTOR. It’s a perfect scale replica of a frontend loader with ingenious functional hydraulic pistons made from wood. I must have this (I love tractors).",
          "href": null
        }
      ],
      "color": "default"
